readable.content: A brown dog is playing with a white and brown dog in a grassy and treed area . A brown dog is rolling over in the grass while a white and brown dog stands next to it . A brown dog lies on its back fighting with a brown and white dog . The two dogs are playing in the yard . Two brown dogs are playing with each other on the grass , with one dog laying on its side .
